{"tid":1540292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇人睇完林鄭講撒回之後重嬲？","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:46:09.000Z","uid":42246,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e82299b80c5affe482e5992affbe473fb003ed","tid":1540292,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母 <br />\n香港人用左咁多血同汗先換到撒回兩隻字<br />\n咁計落去 要換到5大訴求 <br />\n起碼死10000人 20萬人受傷 恆指8000點<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母政府 當人民如草介<br />\n<br />\n今次好好彩 有貿易戰同時打緊 美國又肯搞人權法<br />\n如果今次大家就咁放棄放鬆<br />\n<br />\n雨革之後大家頹左5年 今次大家放棄直接等2047啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a28bf89c9888df414db4c10bc4ab139bbd7cfa","tid":1540292,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"每晚10點 逐個訴求嗌出黎 係逐個叫<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可