-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63d726376d680d0ba1d27832151a124d326d0ec0","tid":1540292,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:02.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n但我唔想每一次都要抗爭政府先會聽我講野<br />\n所以寫左係基本法既雙普選係一定要有！<br />\n若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變做到!<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"5076ee9119395cf899925e2c93d5c8a12a385c87","tid":1540292,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"唔可以再頹落去"},{"pid":"1dcf19e3bfd503039e05d97896dfe594540acbe4","tid":1540292,"uid":59736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"9月8日 美國領事館見"},{"pid":"7d78d2d22caf721c25b58f1ba0d097deec1e9910","tid":1540292,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0204cd44b745cbd9f3d4a5b0fd926ea8eea390","tid":1540292,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"撤"},{"pid":"9dc2af2925ee0d7578a047b18c403d289e77078f","tid":1540292,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a833697aadf1315c6260596eb4ac61185c8877","tid":1540292,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc2af2925ee0d7578a047b18c403d289e77078f","tid":1540292,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T